## Key Concepts

- CSS Grid with explicit breakpoints for 4/2/1 columns
- Flexbox for card content and equal heights
- aspect-ratio and object-fit for header images
- CSS-only hover reveals
- prefers-reduced-motion and focus-visible compliance

## Code Example

```css
