## Why This Question Is Asked
This question tests advanced CSS layout skills, including nested grids, container queries, and motion handling with accessibility considerations in a realistic dashboard scenario.

## Key Concepts
- CSS Grid for orchestrating outer and inner layouts
- Flexbox for aligning panel headers and footers
- CSS container queries enabling responsive sub-grids based on container width
- Entrance staggering animations with accessibility considerations
- Focus-visible outlines for keyboard navigation
- prefers-reduced-motion for respecting user motion preferences

## Code Example
```html
<!-- Dashboard Layout -->
<div class="dashboard">
  <section class="panel">
    <header class="panel-header">...</header>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <!-- Mini-cards grid driven by container queries -->
    </div>
    <footer class="panel-footer">...</footer>
  </section>
  <!-- Additional panels... -->
</div>
```

```css
/* Outer Grid Layout */
.dashboard {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 1rem;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .dashboard {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .dashboard {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

/* Panel Structure */
.panel {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
}

.panel-header,
.panel-footer {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

/* Container Queries for Inner Grid */
.panel-body {
  container-type: inline-size;
}

@container (min-width: 200px) {
  .mini-cards {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

@container (min-width: 350px) {
  .mini-cards {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }
}

@container (min-width: 500px) {
  .mini-cards {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }
}

/* Staggered Entrance Animation */
.panel {
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out forwards;
}

.panel:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0ms; }
.panel:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 100ms; }
.panel:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 200ms; }
.panel:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 300ms; }

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* Accessibility */
:focus-visible {
  outline: 3px solid #2563eb;
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .panel {
    animation: none;
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
```

