## Why This Is Asked
Tests the candidate's ability to design a real-time, per-tenant UI with robust dataflow, per-tenant memoization, and careful rendering to avoid churn during rapid tenant switches.

## Key Concepts
- useSyncExternalStore for external streams per tenant
